text: I tried the Rose Latte earlier today. It was quite tasty for me. 4 stars for it. But the counter staff tried to charge me 50 cents more when I asked for it to be more sweet, which I refused to pay. Instead, I took a few sachets of sugar and paid the normal price. It tasted quite good. I'm not paying you a single cent more for a little more syrup.

Wouldn’t give 5 to this coffee, beans were a little bit over-roasted. (But I’m pretty picky with coffee)

Overall I was happy that they had student discounts and loyalty card :) Personal is super friendly!
Good and strong ice white coffee, great friendly service
Convenient to get a drink on the way to south spine
